1 Day Ago The ministry, popularly known as 'Land of freedom and miracle centre' was shortly after the former Central Bank Governor, Professor Soludo got into office as state governor, marked for demolition in what residents have tagged as a witch-hunt for not supporting him during the governorship election that brought him in November 2021. According to Ejiofor, the governor must condemn in unequivocal terms, the violent attack, molestation and manhandling of Odumeje by his overzealous enforcement officers. See Also






